        WHERE {
            ?godchild :hasGodparent ?godparent .
            ?godparent :hasGender :Male .
        }
    """ .

### goddaughter (female godchild)
:hasGoddaughter a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :hasGodchild ;
    rdfs:label "Has Goddaughter"@en ;
    rdfs:range :FemalePerson ;
    rdfs:comment """Female godchild. 
    Usage: use :hasGodchild for gender-neutral queries."""@en ;
    :MaterializationReason :GenderFirewallLimitation ;
    :MaterializationScript """
